description: Olive Wood Pizza is a mobile pizzeria serving up wood-fired pizza in the Los Angeles and Orange County areas. Olive Wood offers a great variety of toppings, from sausage to jalapeno to potatoes, and each pizza is bound to turn out delicious due to the olive wood firing the oven.Why olive wood? First off, it is a hard wood that burns hot and evenly for a long time, but more importantly, it makes the pizza taste great! Olive wood provides the right amount of smoke, a little sweetness and enough heat to cook the pizzas in just a couple of minutes. With such a great flavor, why not check out Olive Wood Pizza today?
name: Olive Wood Pizza
